# ~/.ssh/config の設定例

```
Host hoge
    HostName hoge.address
    User user
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/hoge_rsa
    LocalForward 1234 hoge:5678
    GatewayPorts yes
    PermitLocalCommand yes
    LocalCommand tmux rename-window \<%n\>

Host fuga
    ProxyCommand ssh -W %h:%p hoge
```

